Eureka!:

Synopsis:
The series tells the story of a young girl inventor who is way ahead of her time. Utilizing creative out-of-the-box thinking, she designs inventions and contraptions in the hopes of making the world a better place and moving her prehistoric community into a more modern era. With the help of her supportive parents, teacher, best friends Pepper and Barry, and beloved pet mammoth Murphy, Eureka is learning to embrace that she is not ordinary… she’s extraordinary.
